ygData.messageBody:
Id like to say Hi too. I play a monk known as Jinsu on the Bertrboxxis

out in the freeport area, although I am looking for a change of scenery.
I am a male and looking to hook up with one of those really cute half even
guys.. They did a real good job those models :) Maybe if this list gets
decent sized someone can make a character list per server so we can atleast
meet that way.

--- Jinsu
